fields.name: admin
docs: Authority allowed to update config parameters.

fields.name: treasury_authority
docs: Authority allowed to withdraw from treasury token accounts.

fields.name: next_vault_id
docs: Vault ID, increments with each new vault.

fields.name: platform_performance_fee_bps
docs: Fee taken from eligble profits above previous high water mark, denoted in basis points.

fields.name: platform_deposit_fee_bps
docs: Fee taken on deposits into vaults, denoted in basis points.

fields.name: platform_withdrawal_fee_bps
docs: Fee taken on withdrawals from vaults, denoted in basis points.

fields.name: platform_referral_fee_bps
docs: INACTIVE - Fee taken on platform fees that will go to referrers, denoted in basis points.

fields.name: status
docs: Determines operational status of the protocol.

fields.name: vault
docs: The vault this strategy belongs to.

fields.name: deposits_deployed
docs: Total deposits deployed to the strategy, denoted in the vault's deposit mint.

fields.name: id
docs: ID unique to the strategy within the vault.

fields.name: strategy_type
docs: Details about the underlying protocol and action of the strategy.

fields.name: authority
docs: Authority of the user account.

fields.name: id
docs: Unique vault ID.

fields.name: authority
docs: Authority allowed to manage the vault.

fields.name: name
docs: Name of the vault (utf8 bytes, padded with 0s).

fields.name: description
docs: Description of the vault (utf8 bytes, padded with 0s).

fields.name: deposit_mint
docs: Mint accepted as vault deposits.

fields.name: _unused0
docs: Unused field, can be reopened.

fields.name: deposit_cap
docs: Max deposits accepted, denoted in deposit mint.

fields.name: user_deposits
docs: Total user deposits, changes on user deposit/withdraw. Denoted in deposit mint.

fields.name: realized_pnl
docs: Total realized profit and loss across all strategies, accumulated on strategy execute/exit, deducted on user withdrawals, excluding fees. Denoted in deposit mint.
Profit and losses are only realized when exiting from strategies and deposits are withdrawn back to vault token accounts.

fields.name: deposits_in_strategies
docs: Total deposits currently allocated in strategies, equals to sum of all Strategy deposits_deployed. Denoted in deposit mint.

fields.name: locked_profit
docs: Currently locked profit amount, denoted in deposit mint.

fields.name: locked_profit_duration
docs: Duration over which depositor's share of vault profit cannot be fully withdrawn.
A longer duration punishes late depositors attempting to front-run vault profits by depositing late and withdrawing at the earliest possible time.

fields.name: last_profit_lock_ts
docs: Last timestamp when profit is recorded.

fields.name: total_shares
docs: Total deposit shares, changes on user deposits and withdrawals.

fields.name: unclaimed_manager_fee
docs: Claimable manager fees, accrues on profitable strategy exits. Denoted in deposit mint.

fields.name: manager_fee_bps
docs: Fee taken from eligble profits above previous high water mark that goes to vault managers, denoted in basis points.

fields.name: status
docs: Determines operational status of the vault.

fields.name: next_strategy_id
docs: Next strategy ID, increments with each new strategy.

fields.name: asset_per_share
docs: Last recorded asset (deposit mint) per share.

fields.name: high_water_mark
docs: All-time highest recorded asset per share.
Fees are only taken on profits above this mark.

fields.name: authority
docs: Authority of the depositor.

fields.name: vault
docs: The vault this depositor is associated with.

fields.name: shares
docs: Total shares of the vault owned by the depositor, denoted in the vault's deposit mint.

fields.name: last_vault_asset_per_share
docs: Last recorded vault asset per share at the time of deposit/withdraw.

fields.name: last_deposit_ts
docs: Timestamp of the last deposit made.

types.name: WrappedI80F48
docs: Borsh serializable wrapper for [`fixed::types::I80F48`].
Calculations are never performed on this type directly as Solana's runtime has limited support for floating operations.
